{"tid":219474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主婦誤殺3個月大兒子判囚八年","createTime":"2017-04-27T08:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T09:50:39.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75277bb81bdebc3d6d6f22d2395930922433671b","tid":219474,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:43:31.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名主婦誤殺三個月大兒子，被判監八年。<br />\n<br />\n被告梁笑芳前年在長洲住所照料其三個月大兒子，疑因抵受不住男嬰不停哭鬧，大力搖晃及掌摑男嬰，男嬰最終死亡，陪審團早前已裁定她誤殺罪成。<br />\n<br />\n法官判刑時指，證據顯示男嬰並非首次被虐，認為保護子女是父母天職，但男嬰卻死於母親手上，而根據被告的心理報告指她曾受家人欺凌，法官拒絕接納作求情理由，判被告監禁八年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=219215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D219215&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5901755d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D219215&h=e150abf2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=219215</a>"},{"pid":"6cd39f663bc49b5017706b95d4fea5abd540fe1e","tid":219474,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"咁就8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0625b5b457a100e4a93c63e8efb7f00237da6960","tid":219474,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:41:26.000Z","msg":"謀殺囉"},{"pid":"0d7b820d0f46fa53b3b2cdec910cf90e1a9aa4f5","tid":219474,"uid":17260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:50:39.000Z","msg":"咁都唔叫謀殺"}]}